---
layout: post
title: Urban Islands
description: Mapping London's Land as 'Urban Islands'
img: /img/coastalv_waterlines_wandsworthlondontest_qgiscoastalv_testii.jpeg
---
  
A project that illustrates how land use can create 'Urban Islands'. It makes use of using waterlines and coastal vignettes, cartographic techniques for illustrating the motion of water and establishing figure-ground. The examples below visualise 2018 Brownfield Register sites as islands.

